  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class AmazonS3ClientBuilder
extends AmazonS3Builder<AmazonS3ClientBuilder,AmazonS3>
    Fluent builder for AmazonS3. Capable of building synchronous and asynchronous clients. Use of the builder is preferred over using constructors of the client class.
